1. *Uhvatite* loptu! (Catch the ball!)
2. Da li *uhvatite* bus na stanici? (Did you catch the bus at the station?)
3. Morate *uhvatiti* priliku dok je još tu. (You have to seize the opportunity while it's still here.)
4. Oni su uspeli *uhvatiti* lopova. (They managed to catch the thief.)
5. Ne mogu *uhvatiti* ritam ove pesme. (I can't catch the rhythm of this song.)
6. *Uhvatite* se za ruke i krenite. (Hold hands and start walking.)
7. Molim vas da *uhvatite* ovu priliku za saradnju. (Please take this opportunity to cooperate.)
8. *Uhvatite* se u koštac sa tim problemom. (Tackle that problem head-on.)
9. Kada sam ga videla, *uhvatila* sam ga za ruku. (When I saw him, I grabbed his hand.)
10. Vreme je da *uhvatite* svoju budućnost u svoje ruke. (It's time to take your future into your own hands.)

Note: The word "uhvatite" is the imperative form of the verb "uhvatiti" which means "to catch" or "to grab" in English. The word "uhvatite" is used in different contexts and positions in the above sentences.